<a href="http://europa.eu/rapid/pressReleasesAction.do?reference=MEMO/09/483&amp;format=HTML&amp;aged=0&amp;language=EN&amp;guiLanguage=en" target="_self">http://europa.eu/rapid/pressReleasesAction.do?reference=MEMO/09/483&amp;...</a></p><p>
CE, blog de la Commissaire Mariann Fischer Boel, 29 octobre 2009<br/>
